name: My Surreal Path In Surreal Dreams

metadata.name: Daydream
metadata.description:
When I find myself in a state of sorrow, I close my eyes and step into an endless field full of jade-colored grass and ocean sky in the middle of all living things. Then I feel that I have found my inner peace and a door to my soul.

Artwork Details:  Printable 57x57cm.

Softwares Used:  Photoshop  + Illustrator.
